name: What a Bountiful Harvest, Demon Lord!
author: UpdatingStatusOnGoingTypeManhwa
content: I&#039ve become the Demon Lord, the Final Boss in a game, but...If I invade the human world? I&#039ll be slain by the Max-level Protagonist I raised.If I stop the invasion? I&#039ll be devoured by my starving Demon Generals....Therefore, the only answer is farming.Orginal Webtoon: Naver Webtoon, Naver Series
